snippet.textDisplay: One problem with the English translation was that when it says “Maharoo maharoo mahjabeen mahjabeen” the meaning of those words are actually different. Those are Persian words, maharoo means adorable and mahjabeen means something worth being treasured. I know this because my sister’s name is Mehree and my name is Mahjubeh. We were born in Iran and our parents gave us Persian names.
